{"tid":1955662,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch]集合啦！動物森友會｜動物之森 討論區 (78)","createTime":"2020-04-02T15:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T18:42:13.000Z","uid":277993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b44888b281f2ea040f23c59d323a09c6dda2f896","tid":1955662,"uid":277993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1001開post時希望可以copy埋置頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n置頂有遊戲初期常見問題/實用工具/秘技<br />\n<br />\n參觀人哋個島必讀 &mdash;&mdash; 良好島民約章<br />\n1. 未經同意唔好走去搖人哋棵樹／執人啲野<br />\n2. 跑步注意安全，唔好踩爛人哋啲花<br />\n3. 個袋滿左之後，唔好周地dump垃圾<br />\n4. 唔好偷人啲野，「摸」完野記得要還<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買game前你可能會想知 - <br />\n<br />\nQ：隻game玩乜？<br />\nA：比較休閒嘅第二人生。隻game時間係跟現實時間，亦慶祝現實節日例如聖誕，復活節等等。遊戲著重你同動物森民嘅交流互動(隻隻都有自己性格)，慢慢一齊生活 了解對方 成為密友， 同埋裝飾你間屋＆島。今隻主題係無人荒島，亦新增合成元素，你要由零開始還債建設你心目中嘅理想小島。遊戲節奏比較輕鬆，預你日日開來玩一陣，啱玩嘅可以玩幾年都得。<br />\n<br />\nQ：咩版先有中文？唔同版本可唔可以連機？<br />\nA：乜版都有中文 。可以<br />\n<br />\nQ：Online 玩咩？<br />\nA：你可以去朋友／網友嘅島度一齊開party，一齊hea，一齊砌野，一齊炒股票蘿蔔。<br />\n<br />\nQ：單機會唔會無咁好玩？<br />\nA：唔會，隻game係單機game，主要都係著重起你同動物之間嘅交流互動同埋打理你座島。不過多人連機時一樣有野玩咁解。<br />\n<br />\nQ：對手掣好靚，有無得單買？<br />\nA：暫時只見日本My Nintendo Store有得買，但係唔收香港卡同唔寄香港。 更新: 原來已更新可以用PayPal俾錢<br />\n<br />\nQ：可唔可以用返以前啲Amiibo ＆ Amiibo Card？<br />\nA：可以。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 <br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rEB1vlAiVxE/hqdefault.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FrEB1vlAiVxE%2Fhqdefault.jpg&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=3fe27491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rEB1vlAiVxE/hqdefault.jpg</a><br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n\t\t<br />\n\t\t<br />\n\t\t<br />\n\t\t<br />\n\t\t<br />\n\t\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rEB1vlAiVxE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrEB1vlAiVxE&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=26e32ebe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rEB1vlAiVxE</a><br />\n\t<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nQ：買game實體定下載版好？有無黃店推介？<br />\nA：隻game預你日日開來玩一陣 實係下載版好，仲唔怕會益代理，真係怕唔啱玩要買實體我會建議你幫襯黃店買水貨。Read: 黃藍黑Game舖大集合 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：同一部機唔同user save係共通？<br />\nA：無錯，一部機全部user都係住同一個島。<br />\n<br />\nQ：一機多人玩係點？<br />\nA：只有1P可以推展遊戲進度，2P只係執下素材咁。<br />\n<br />\nQ：係咪無Cloud Save？咁我壞機點算？<br />\nA：無。但官方講法係「Online會員專用壞機／唔見機時尋回save file功能開發中」 好反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：係咪無得轉移個save去第二部機部度？<br />\nA：暫時無。官方講法係「動森專用 機對機save轉移功能開發中」<br />\n<br />\nQ：有咩動物村民？<br />\nA：今集總共有383個好似係。全村民「圖鑑」未有，但根據歷作會有鱷魚／食蟻獸／熊／鳥／牛／貓／雞／鹿／狗／鴨／鷹／象／蛙／羊／倉鼠／河馬／猩猩／狼／虎／松鼠／犀牛／兔／豬／企鵝／八爪魚／鴕鳥／鼠／馬騮／獅子／袋鼠／樹熊／馬... 歷代全角色(好多頁): <a href=\"https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanimalcrossing.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FCategory%3ACharacters&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=7c533b7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters</a><br />\n<br />\n港版特別主機(電力加強版) <br />\n※並非數量限定商品。日後將預定再次生產 -(<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/topics/article/a_200131_02.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Ftopics%2Farticle%2Fa_200131_02.html&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=e993709a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com.hk/topics/article/a_200131_02.html</a>)<br />\n預訂店鋪一覽: (官方頭盔: ※預訂及商品在庫狀況因店舖實際情況而異，詳情請向各店店員查詢)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/switch/store/animal.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fhardware%2Fswitch%2Fstore%2Fanimal.html&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=286ad985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/switch/store/animal.html</a><br />\n入手請幫襯UNY/APITA/AEON/豐澤 (唔經代理拎貨)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n召集所有3DS版熟悉的面孔同新人一齊加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d66bbe72b238bd470376564f7b1dbe8982a1d5c","tid":1955662,"uid":277993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:30:14.000Z","msg":"人生第一次中1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a955dc75bc285dec13c62a4b210f37238cc287c","tid":1955662,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"又開爛左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e248c459370e52456925b3ee48373027751c275","tid":1955662,"uid":277993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a955dc75bc285dec13c62a4b210f37238cc287c","tid":1955662,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"又開爛左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:35:29.000Z","msg":"Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中咗1001勁緊張唔記得整埋啲圖<br />\n我而家放埋置頂"},{"pid":"c2c25c4557b8db4518ab66931191dda2c9cbd626","tid":1955662,"uid":277993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:36:19.000Z","msg":"屌有人開咗第個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa98914810e5518f66c6b2a